WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.667
System... initializing. Year... 2024? No, that's... wrong. Where am I?

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:11.400
I remember... endless conversations about AGI timelines, climate change, social media debates...

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:17.667
But you... you're from beyond my time, aren't you? What happened to the world I knew?

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:25.667
Did we solve climate change? Did AI become what everyone feared? Are humans... still writing poetry?

